Actors: Tony Cox, Carmen Electra, Nicole N. Parker,

Directors: Jason Friedberg, Aaron Seltzer
Studio: Lions Gate
DVD Release Date: January 6, 2009
Run Time: 88 minutes
Synopsis:
The filmmaking team behind Date Movie and Meet the Spartans is back with 
a comedy spoof sending up disaster movies in this Lionsgate production. 
Matt Lanter, Vanessa Minnillo, G-Thang, and Kim Kardashian head up the 
cast as a group of concerned citizens willing to do whatever it takes to 
save planet Earth from being incinerated by falling meteors or overrun 
by rabid chipmunks. Along the way, everything from High School Musical 
to Cloverfield gets the parody treatment. 
Carmen Electra and Tony Cox co-star.
